1
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,400
This matter

2
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,360
will ruin your future sooner or later

3
00:01:22,839 --> 00:01:24,160
and hold you back.

4
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,239
So,

5
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,480
all the blame

6
00:01:28,639 --> 00:01:30,239
will be taken by Dad.

7
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:34,040
Just let it all go.

8
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:35,519
Dad.

9
00:01:37,919 --> 00:01:39,279
I'm here to see you off one last time.

10
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,000
I think I should

11
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,440
say my final goodbye to him.

12
00:02:11,839 --> 00:02:12,880
And you.

13
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,800
I want this company,

14
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:18,880
and Lin Jiaqi.

15
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,600
So I'm going to make everything public.

16
00:02:24,839 --> 00:02:26,080
I will tell everyone

17
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:29,039
