18
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,520
No, what do you mean?

19
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,440
What?

20
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,639
Didn't we agree on this before?

21
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:02,960
Okay.

22
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,240
We'll head over right now.

23
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,600
What's wrong?

24
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,639
President Gu,

25
00:03:06,839 --> 00:03:07,600
