28
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,960
before transferring the rest of the funds.

29
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,039
If they don't transfer the money,

30
00:03:15,679 --> 00:03:17,000
how do we pay the contract fees to our partners?

31
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,240
What does this have to do

32
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:20,759
with the clinical trial results?

33
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,080
Why are

34
00:03:26,279 --> 00:03:27,160
the clinical trial results

35
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,199
coming out so slowly this time?

36
00:03:30,399 --> 00:03:31,279
I heard...

37
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,639
I heard it's an order from above.

38
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,839
They said they want to add

39
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:36,399
more items to the clinical trial results.

40
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:39,039
I really find it strange this time.

41
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,800
All the relevant departments

42
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,199
are being exceptionally harsh on us.

43
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,279
There were never this many procedures before.

44
00:03:50,119 --> 00:03:51,559
I'm afraid we're in trouble this time.

45
00:03:58,759 --> 00:04:00,320
No, what's going on?

46
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,639
These investors are going too far.

47
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,240
We've waited so long and they're still not here.

48
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,399
They must be doing this on purpose.

49
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,360
That's still too much.

50
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,440
We've been waiting for two hours.

51
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,960
Back when we were the investors,

52
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,279
