53
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:14,919
When discussing business,

54
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,200
have we ever been this late?

55
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,160
I just feel something is strange.

56
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,320
Something feels a bit off.

57
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:23,320
Qi Shuai,

58
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:24,399
do you think

59
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,040
something might have happened?

60
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:27,920
How about this,

61
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,000
I'll make another call

62
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,040
to see what exactly

63
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,399
is going on over there.

64
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:37,480
Excuse me.

65
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,239
Why is it you?

66
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:45,600
Watch your tone.

67
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,799
This is our company's

68
00:04:46,799 --> 00:04:47,799
new president.

69
00:04:48,359 --> 00:04:49,000
What did you say?

70
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,640
Let me introduce myself.

71
00:04:51,359 --> 00:04:53,040
I am the one acquiring Chunhao Group this time,

72
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,399
the head of Rosenmoss,

73
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,799
Feng Ziang.

74
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,320
President Gu

75
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,679
Look how considerate I am.

76
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,160
Just so you can enjoy your meal in peace,

77
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,160
I had everyone I brought with me

78
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,359
