79
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,920
Are you trying to provoke me?

80
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,880
What provocation?

81
00:05:22,679 --> 00:05:23,679
That's such a harsh word.

82
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,119
This is a warning.

83
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,640
Just get to the point.

84
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,600
I hate beating around the bush.

85
00:05:32,119 --> 00:05:33,720
You still haven't come to your senses, have you?

86
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:35,880
Are you currently

87
00:05:36,239 --> 00:05:37,959
completely clueless about the situation?

88
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,600
Then I'll be straightforward.

89
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,279
If by next week,

90
00:05:42,679 --> 00:05:43,799
Feimanchi still hasn't produced

91
00:05:43,799 --> 00:05:44,959
the samples for the new product,

92
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,720
not only will you not receive the remaining investment,

93
00:05:48,799 --> 00:05:50,160
but to protect our company's interests,

94
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,760
we will also demand that you

95
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:53,079
pay back double the deposit already paid.

96
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,239
President Gu,

97
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:56,799
I heard that for the new product project,

98
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:59,040
you even sold your real estate in the US.

99
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,839
I'm truly touched.

100
00:06:02,679 --> 00:06:04,720
So, regarding Feimanchi's bonds next,

101
00:06:05,239 --> 00:06:07,079
