102
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:11,079
It sounds really tough.

103
00:06:12,799 --> 00:06:13,359
Very soon,

104
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,760
I'm afraid you'll become completely penniless.

105
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,880
Seeing you now, I finally understand

106
00:06:23,359 --> 00:06:25,040
how annoying I used to be.

107
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,359
President Gu,

108
00:06:29,239 --> 00:06:30,799
given that we've worked together before,

109
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,880
there are some things I still need to tell you.

110
00:06:33,559 --> 00:06:34,559
If I were you,

111
00:06:35,559 --> 00:06:37,640
