112
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,160
I'd hurry up and go make some money.

113
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:44,079
When you were in my current position back then,

114
00:06:44,559 --> 00:06:45,720
did it feel really good?

115
00:06:46,799 --> 00:06:47,399
Gu Tiancheng,

116
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,600
the power you once had

117
00:06:50,239 --> 00:06:51,320
wasn't because of who you are,

118
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,720
but because of your position.

119
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,959
But now you have nothing.

120
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:57,799
You, as a person,

121
00:06:58,559 --> 00:06:59,959
are completely worthless.

122
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,200
I want to remind you of one thing.

123
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,399
With your current capabilities,

124
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,959
to take down me, Gu Tiancheng,

125
00:07:08,679 --> 00:07:09,920
I'm afraid you're still far from it.

126
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,239
I'm so pissed.

127
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,480
Tell me,

128
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,320
why didn't I think of that?

129
00:07:29,119 --> 00:07:30,559
Buying out the investment company,

130
00:07:30,559 --> 00:07:32,040
then interfering with the new product.

131
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:34,040
Isn't that my usual trick?

132
00:07:34,359 --> 00:07:35,040
That brat,

133
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,359
how dare he plagiarize me

134
00:07:36,559 --> 00:07:37,559
without paying royalties?

135
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,880
Now we really have no way out.

136
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,760
What if we

137
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:51,359
cancel the investment contract?

138
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:53,920
You must be joking.

139
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,200
Are you serious?

140
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,480
No way.

141
00:08:00,559 --> 00:08:01,200
Let me tell you,

142
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,239
absolutely not, President Gu.

143
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,720
Let me get this straight.

144
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,440
Well,

145
00:08:12,679 --> 00:08:14,040
let's not even talk about the contract penalty.

146
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,160
Just the fact that Rosenmoss

147
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,160
is involved in this,

148
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,239
everyone will know soon enough.

149
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,440
When that happens,

150
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,679
none of us can bear the responsibility, right?

151
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,000
And by then,

152
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,279
without an investor,

153
00:08:23,359 --> 00:08:24,679
funding will be the biggest problem.

154
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:26,920
We have nothing left to sell!

155
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,559
The top priority right now

156
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:31,559
is to make sure

157
00:08:31,559 --> 00:08:33,039
the workers in the company and factory

158
00:08:33,119 --> 00:08:33,960
