159
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:36,159
Come on,

160
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,000
at a time like this,

161
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,919
you're still worrying about them?

162
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,679
We're about to end up under a bridge

163
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,440
