164
00:08:40,719 --> 00:08:41,239
Shut up.

165
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,760
I'm thinking.

166
00:08:43,719 --> 00:08:44,080
By the way,

167
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,359
about this matter,

168
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,440
especially to Lin Jiaqi,

169
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,159
don't say a single word.

170
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:54,760
I heard Feimanchi's new product

171
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,119
already has a set production date.

172
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:57,919
It seems

173
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,640
they're going to produce on schedule.

174
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:00,719
That's right.

175
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,080
Leaving this matter to you

176
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,239
really saves me a lot of worry.

177
00:09:04,599 --> 00:09:05,359
Thanks for the compliment.

178
00:09:07,599 --> 00:09:09,080
Everything is under my control.

179
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,039
Their struggles

180
00:09:11,599 --> 00:09:12,320
