181
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,000
That's true.

182
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,719
How is the situation with Tan Feng now?

183
00:09:35,719 --> 00:09:36,960
Basically, there are no problems.

184
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,239
And the case

185
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,320
is almost closed.

186
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,239
Rest assured.

187
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,400
I figure

188
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,039
that kid won't make any big moves anymore.

189
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,760
Don't let your guard down.

190
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,840
You should keep an eye on him.

191
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,400
There can't be any mistakes.

192
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,400
Also,

193
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:55,520
I need to trouble you with one more thing.

194
00:09:57,479 --> 00:09:58,880
Help me thoroughly investigate

195
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,280
Gu Tiancheng of Feimanchi.

196
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:02,799
Use whatever means necessary.

197
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,080
Whether it's his relationships with women

198
00:10:05,359 --> 00:10:06,960
or his financial dealings with others,

199
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,119
find out everything.

200
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,080
Don't miss a single detail.

201
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,200
Okay.

202
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,239
I understand.

203
00:10:15,479 --> 00:10:16,080
You must find

204
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,640
a fatal weakness to completely destroy this man.

205
00:10:18,719 --> 00:10:19,440
As soon as you have intel,

206
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,599
notify me immediately.

207
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,320
Don't worry.

208
00:10:22,479 --> 00:10:23,119
I got it.

209
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,119
Thanks for your hard work.

210
00:10:58,479 --> 00:10:59,479
Peeking at me?

211
00:11:01,479 --> 00:11:02,359
You scared me.

212
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,599
Honestly,

213
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,239
were you

214
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,080
captivated by my good looks?

215
00:11:09,119 --> 00:11:10,400
I saw you lying here all alone,

216
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,400
