217
00:11:11,479 --> 00:11:13,000
So I brought you some cold medicine.

218
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,000
I was just taking

219
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,159
a quick nap on the couch.

220
00:11:16,719 --> 00:11:17,760
Actually, when you just came in,

221
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,440
I was already awake.

222
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,840
Couldn't the sound of the door closing

223
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,000
