224
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,840
Then why were you pretending to be asleep?

225
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,119
Seeing you always falling asleep on the couch lately,

226
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,320
are you not sleeping well at home?

227
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,119
With so many things going on lately,

228
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,000
after I go home,

229
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,479
it's so empty with just me alone.

230
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,400
So I just

231
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,239
can't sleep well.

232
00:11:41,479 --> 00:11:42,880
I brought you some citrus.

233
00:11:43,359 --> 00:11:44,359
It's very effective for insomnia.

234
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:45,400
Okay.

235
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:48,280
I know a lot has happened at the company lately,

236
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,159
but I don't know how to help you.

237
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:52,799
So,

238
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,479
I can only care for you more in daily life.

239
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,799
Then what if

240
00:12:00,799 --> 00:12:02,320
I want you to do something for me,

241
00:12:02,359 --> 00:12:03,039
would you be willing to?

242
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,640
What is it?

243
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,679
I want to cure my illness.

244
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,280
Why are your hands so cold?

245
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,080
Is it because you're too busy with work

246
00:12:26,719 --> 00:12:27,640
and haven't been eating well?

247
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,799
Can you just stay still like this,

248
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,840
and let your healing power

249
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:45,640
slowly soothe me bit by bit?

250
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,359
Officer Lin.

251
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:55,080
I know why you

252
00:12:55,359 --> 00:12:56,039
came to see me.

253
00:12:56,599 --> 00:12:57,479
Just tell me directly.

254
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:58,239
Alright.

255
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,320
Then I'll get straight to the point.

256
00:13:01,599 --> 00:13:02,320
Today,

257
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,479
I'm here to go over the statement

258
00:13:03,479 --> 00:13:04,440
confirmation with you.

259
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,479
Take a look,

260
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,960
and then sign it.

261
00:13:22,719 --> 00:13:23,520
Officer Lin,

262
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:25,840
