263
00:13:26,119 --> 00:13:26,799
How is it going?

264
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,960
You know about Feng Wei's suicide, right?

265
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:31,840
I didn't know.

266
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,440
He left a confession letter.

267
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,679
It clearly recorded

268
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,799
