269
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:41,440
So that's what happened.

270
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:44,000
It seems that while I was in a coma,

271
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,320
a lot of things really happened.

272
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:48,640
You bet.

273
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,799
I mean, why were you hiding back then?

274
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:52,840
What was there to run from?

275
00:13:53,599 --> 00:13:54,280
Do you have any idea

276
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,919
how badly my superiors scolded me?

277
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:57,799
I'm sorry,

278
00:13:58,039 --> 00:13:58,799
Officer Lin.

279
00:13:59,520 --> 00:13:59,840
I...

280
00:14:00,119 --> 00:14:01,359
I caused trouble for your work.

281
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:03,440
Will you guys

282
00:14:04,359 --> 00:14:05,559
