290
00:14:20,239 --> 00:14:22,400
Once your body is fully recovered,

291
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:23,880
you still have to come with me

292
00:14:24,119 --> 00:14:25,239
to the station.

293
00:14:28,239 --> 00:14:28,960
Hello, Uncle Du.

294
00:14:29,239 --> 00:14:29,840
What's wrong?

295
00:14:30,159 --> 00:14:30,799
Jiaqi,

296
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,440
something happened.

297
00:14:32,119 --> 00:14:33,440
The production line at the Tongzhou factory

298
00:14:33,679 --> 00:14:34,799
has completely stopped.

299
00:14:35,599 --> 00:14:36,320
Don't worry.

300
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,159
Take your time.

301
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,200
The main issue is the raw material supply.

302
00:14:39,679 --> 00:14:41,400
Can you think of another way on your end?

303
00:14:42,359 --> 00:14:42,840
What?

304
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:49,159
We can't

305
00:14:49,239 --> 00:14:51,000
start the first round of production? What do you mean?

306
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,320
Our company's new product

307
00:14:54,599 --> 00:14:55,880
mainly uses vanilla as a raw material.

308
00:14:56,359 --> 00:14:57,840
And the company that supplies the vanilla

309
00:14:58,119 --> 00:14:59,200
has now cut off the supply.

310
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,760
Right now, the factory

311
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,919
can't start working.

312
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,359
The workers don't know what to do either.

313
00:15:05,719 --> 00:15:06,760
But how could they suddenly

314
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,080
unilaterally cut off the supply?

315
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:09,479
That company...

316
00:15:09,479 --> 00:15:10,599
haven't we been working with them for a long time?

317
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:12,719
Why would they suddenly cut it off?

318
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,080
I don't know what's going on either.

319
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:17,200
This company is quite reliable,

320
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:18,679
otherwise we wouldn't have

321
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:19,760
kept working with them until now.

322
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,159
If they can't supply the goods,

323
00:15:23,239 --> 00:15:24,640
then they'll have to pay the contract penalty.

324
00:15:25,679 --> 00:15:26,799
The compensation is completely useless.

325
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:29,000
If we can't start production today,

326
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,440
we'll have to compensate Rosenmoss

327
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,159
for their investment.

328
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,919
Compared to the compensation,

329
00:15:33,359 --> 00:15:34,359
the investment is much more important.

330
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,479
Then what should we do now?

331
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,400
Try hard to persuade the supplier.

332
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,440
Come with me.

333
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:40,159
Let's go.

334
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,640
Rest assured,

335
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:45,520
as for the contract penalty, according to the contract,

336
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,280
we will compensate you in full.

337
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:48,359
President Gu,

338
00:15:48,599 --> 00:15:49,280
you should go back.

339
00:15:49,599 --> 00:15:50,080
President Zhu,

340
00:15:50,479 --> 00:15:51,400
I think you're mistaken.

341
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,679
We didn't come here to ask for the contract penalty.

342
00:15:54,119 --> 00:15:56,000
We hope you can continue to supply us.

343
00:15:56,719 --> 00:15:57,640
With something like this happening,

344
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,280
we at least need to know the reason.

345
00:16:00,479 --> 00:16:02,200
Did Feng Ziang make you do this?

346
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:05,440
Feng Ziang is really going too far.

347
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,280
He's becoming someone I don't recognize anymore.

348
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:08,520
I'm afraid

349
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:10,760
the despicable things Feng Ziang has done

350
00:16:11,359 --> 00:16:12,559
are far more than just this.

351
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:21,840
Hello, Weiwei.

352
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,359
The people from Rosenmoss are here.

353
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:25,320
They said they want to look into the production halt.

354
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:27,760
They also demanded a meeting within thirty minutes.

355
00:16:28,239 --> 00:16:29,239
What should we do, Jiaqi?

356
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,119
You and President Gu need to come back quickly.

357
00:16:31,799 --> 00:16:32,919
Okay, I got it.

358
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,719
What's wrong?

359
00:16:34,719 --> 00:16:35,760
The people from Rosenmoss are here.

360
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:37,039
Let's go.

361
00:16:50,559 --> 00:16:51,320
Listen, Director Feng.

362
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,960
You don't have a secret crush on me, do you?

363
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,000
Why are you copying me in everything?

364
00:16:56,239 --> 00:16:56,880
Go ahead.

365
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,239
Did you come here today

366
00:16:58,520 --> 00:16:59,280
to have a meeting with me,

367
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:00,080
or to catch up like old friends?

368
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,719
President Gu.

369
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:03,559
I'm just telling it like it is.

370
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,479
I heard

371
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,640
you haven't even gotten the permits from the relevant departments,

372
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,560
and you can't proceed with production on schedule.

373
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,199
Look at you.

374
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:13,199
Instead of sticking to your debt collection job,

375
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,079
why bother running a company?

376
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,880
Failing to produce on schedule is a breach of contract.

377
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:19,560
I'll give you two more weeks.

378
00:17:20,719 --> 00:17:21,719
If you can't start production,

379
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,920
you either repay the investment funds,

380
00:17:24,959 --> 00:17:26,280
or hand over the production rights for the new product

381
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:27,400
to Rosenmoss.

382
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,880
What's wrong, President Gu?

383
00:17:34,119 --> 00:17:34,800
Nothing to say?

384
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,040
Don't be nervous.

385
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:39,359
Both of these options are pretty good.

386
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:41,959
How about

387
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:43,199
you guys discuss it?

388
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,000
This scene

389
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,199
is really giving me déjà vu.

390
00:17:52,119 --> 00:17:53,760
When Director Feng came to the company this time,

391
00:17:54,119 --> 00:17:55,119
that whole scene

392
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:57,239
was exactly like the scene when President Gu came to the company

393
00:17:57,239 --> 00:17:58,040
back then.

394
00:17:58,839 --> 00:17:59,520
Jiaqi,

395
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,280
what's wrong with you today?

396
00:18:01,839 --> 00:18:02,800
You look so down.

397
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,959
How can I be happy?

398
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,959
Feng Ziang coming to the company this time

399
00:18:06,959 --> 00:18:08,439
is definitely to make things difficult for us.

400
00:18:09,079 --> 00:18:10,959
I don't know what President Gu is going to do.

401
00:18:11,119 --> 00:18:13,000
President Gu definitely knows what to do.

402
00:18:13,119 --> 00:18:14,359
As the saying goes,

403
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,959
whoever tied the bell must untie it.

404
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:17,199
Our President Gu

405
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:19,000
has experienced all these tricks before.

406
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,040
So,

407
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,199
don't worry about it.

408
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,119
You two are really good at comforting people.

409
00:18:24,319 --> 00:18:25,280
Alright, let's go.

410
00:18:25,359 --> 00:18:26,000
Let's go, let's go.

411
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:39,040
I announce that

412
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,760
Rosenmoss will send a seconded director

413
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:42,680
to be stationed at Feimanchi.

414
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:47,400
Director Hu,

415
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,640
who do you think

416
00:18:49,959 --> 00:18:50,920
they will send?

417
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,520
Feng Ziang.

418
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,760
You really like copying me.

419
00:19:04,079 --> 00:19:05,199
I doubt you even know

420
00:19:05,199 --> 00:19:06,439
who you are anymore.

421
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:07,560
President Gu,

422
00:19:07,959 --> 00:19:09,319
since you put it that way,

423
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,640
I'll just copy you a bit more.

424
00:19:12,839 --> 00:19:14,439
I want Lin Jiaqi to be my secretary.

425
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:21,280
What did you say?

426
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,599
President Gu,

427
00:19:23,239 --> 00:19:24,239
why are you angry?

428
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,640
The seconded director's right to appoint and dismiss

429
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,520
is at their own discretion.

430
00:19:28,719 --> 00:19:30,119
This is the rule you set.

431
00:19:37,439 --> 00:19:38,760
What exactly do you want?

432
00:19:42,079 --> 00:19:43,119
I remember telling you

433
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,959
that in this position,

434
00:19:45,959 --> 00:19:47,160
every word you ever said,

435
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,680
I would return to you verbatim.

436
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:51,359
Lin Jiaqi is my personal secretary.

437
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:53,439
I won't give her to you.

438
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,079
What?

439
00:19:54,719 --> 00:19:55,439
You want to breach the contract?

440
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:56,719
No matter what you say,

441
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,239
I won't give Lin Jiaqi to you.

442
00:20:00,959 --> 00:20:02,000
As a person in charge,

443
00:20:02,839 --> 00:20:04,199
you must be able to protect those around you.

444
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:05,839
President Gu,

445
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,640
you really say one thing and do another.

446
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,560
If you don't agree,

447
00:20:11,239 --> 00:20:12,800
how will you protect your employees?

448
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:15,760
It seems Lin Jiaqi

449
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:18,040
either has exceptional work abilities,

450
00:20:19,439 --> 00:20:20,239
or

451
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:22,119
you have special feelings for her.

452
00:20:26,079 --> 00:20:27,280
Are you really going to, for her sake,

453
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:30,000
drag all 4,500 employees of the company down?

454
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,640
How are you qualified to be the president like this?

455
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,959
Feng Ziang, don't push me.

456
00:20:34,239 --> 00:20:34,760
President Gu.

457
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:37,800
Say no more.

458
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,040
I'll go.

459
00:20:39,319 --> 00:20:40,079
Lin Jiaqi.

460
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:43,800
I think Mr. Feng makes sense.

461
00:20:45,199 --> 00:20:46,520
We shouldn't, just for me,

462
00:20:46,959 --> 00:20:48,680
affect so many people in the company.

463
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,239
It's not worth it.

464
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:51,719
You work for me.

465
00:20:51,719 --> 00:20:52,599
I decide whether you stay or go.

466
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:53,560
President Gu,

467
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:57,280
don't mix personal feelings with work.

468
00:21:00,479 --> 00:21:01,880
Let's just follow the contract.

469
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,520
Since the contract says

470
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,959
the seconded director has the right to appoint and dismiss,

471
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:07,920
then

472
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:09,640
Feimanchi

473
00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:11,880
should respect Mr. Feng's authority.
